OL,3,CTrust criticised over treatment of 12
OL,4,Cwomen in cervical screening scandal
OL,6,FThe Southern Health Trust is facing
OL,7,Ffresh criticism after audits found
OL,8,Fserious failings in the care of 12
OL,9,Fwomen, who were all diagnosed with
OL,10,Fcervical cancer after their smear
OL,11,Ftests were wrongly read.
OL,13,FSerious Adverse Incident reports were
OL,14,Fcommissioned following the completion
OL,15,Fof an Invasive Cancer Audit for the 12
OL,16,Fwomen in the Southern Trust over the
OL,17,F2018 to 2024 period.
