OL,6,FThe SAI reports, which were delivered
OL,7,Fto the women yesterday, said that they
OL,8,Fwere failed due to the
OL,9,Funderperformance of some screeners.
OL,11,FIt said that due to staffing issues
OL,12,Ftwo screeners "did substantial amounts
OL,13,Fof poorly monitored overtime," which,
OL,14,Fthe review team said, "contributed to
OL,15,Fthe poor performance over a period of
OL,16,Fyears."
OL,18,FThe team also found "poor management
OL,19,Fof underperformance" in the laboratory
OL,20,Fand a lack of senior management
OL,21,Foversight of the laboratory.
