OL,6,FReferring to the Public Health Agency,
OL,7,Fthe report said that "oversight by the
OL,8,FPHA was at lab level, rather than
OL,9,Findividual screener performance."
OL,11,FThe review team said "this led to poor
OL,12,Fperformance going unquestioned" and
OL,13,Fsaid that "earlier intervention would
OL,14,Fhave raised a red flag."
OL,16,FThe report also said this is a
OL,17,Flearning that a "small number of
OL,18,Funderperforming staff can impact
OL,19,Foverall laboratory standards and have
OL,20,Fsuch a devastating impact on the
OL,21,Fhealth and wellbeing of patients."
