OL,6,FIn a statement the Southern Health
OL,7,FTrust said: "The SAI review team
OL,8,Fexamined the clinical records,
OL,9,Flaboratory records, PHA policies,
OL,10,FTrust policies and all relevant
OL,11,Fguidance relating to cervical
OL,12,Fscreening to inform this report.
OL,14,F"The Trust has now shared the draft
OL,15,Fwritten report directly with patients
OL,16,Fand families involved and are seeking
OL,17,Ftheir comments. We apologise again to
OL,18,Fany woman and their family affected by
OL,19,Fpast failures in our cervical
OL,20,Fscreening processes.
